{"tid":1183252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日隻狗走左....無奈","createTime":"2019-06-02T18:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T16:52:57.000Z","uid":194743,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f6cd4773da605182452600bde00cd3813f7ea978","tid":1183252,"uid":194743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:56:52.000Z","msg":"見到佢爬左係度....即係去左動物醫院<br />\n醫生即為佢量體溫 血壓....整左30分鐘...<br />\n我離開左醫院一陣...即收到醫院電話叫我返去..<br />\n醫生即要我決定打唔打強心針....佢話打左其實都冇用...狗果腦都傷左...救返都變植物...<br />\n諗下諗下其實都係過左10~15秒左右.....佢直情係面前冇埋心跳.....<br />\n好後悔當初冇叫醫生打左枝針先再諗....話唔定有奇蹟...唉<br />\n<br />\n呢度有冇獸醫ching係度....解釋下有冇更好既decision係呢D情況...<br />\n果刻真係反應唔切..."},{"pid":"4649e9c96096e9521ca9524bb6f2d9e21df6c747","tid":1183252,"uid":194743,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:58:42.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係害死佢.........冇左心跳之後仲係度嘔返胃....唉"},{"pid":"51e9f5d135b88cd6dae60b01915bdca5dfdd93d3","tid":1183252,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:00:58.000Z","msg":"有暗病，rip"},{"pid":"04c3160f7bd6c290623b0ded1618037b271feb92","tid":1183252,"uid":194743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"51e9f5d135b88cd6dae60b01915bdca5dfdd93d3","tid":1183252,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:00:58.000Z","msg":"有暗病，rip"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:03:12.000Z","msg":"唔係.....<br />\n體溫40.5度<br />\n初步估計係中暑....佢係室外跑.....<br />\n想去城大驗....但驗完會冇左個遺體....同埋都走左...最尾冇去而家都唔知咩事...."},{"pid":"7753b9d083fa30b98c284a6415d944baac4fccac","tid":1183252,"uid":194743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:03:59.000Z","msg":"大家都係小心D狗中暑, 發生左之後上網睇返狗中暑會好麻煩 同危險<br />\n就黎夏天..."},{"pid":"cdb5be4e3e109e1bf6b0db4155da9101df3cd6e7","tid":1183252,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:10:07.000Z","msg":"生死有命"},{"pid":"9bb9b64a31a1eba8bfbe17ea479e04af9949e6ed","tid":1183252,"uid":194743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdb5be4e3e109e1bf6b0db4155da9101df3cd6e7","tid":1183252,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:10:07.000Z","msg":"生死有命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:16:18.000Z","msg":"係....<br />\n但之後諗返如果打左枝強心針....心跳冇停....就算變左植物打住吊液可能有1日會起返身....但唔打枝針死硬....最後都沒諗到係面前冇左心跳......生命真係好脆弱.......有冇獸醫巴絲話我知狗狗如果中重暑其實有冇機會救返......變左植物後會唔會有奇蹟有1日會起返身...."},{"pid":"91980c101baa16a3833f2aa694f952acde969729","tid":1183252,"uid":54791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:32:41.000Z","msg":"唔好怪自己，無論你點樣決定，都唔應該後悔"},{"pid":"ef7520d813e3a2acb2aae43eac6f98bd44e193ec","tid":1183252,"uid":194743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"91980c101baa16a3833f2aa694f952acde969729","tid":1183252,"uid":54791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:32:41.000Z","msg":"唔好怪自己，無論你點樣決定，都唔應該後悔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T19:44:07.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<br />\n但真係好心嗡..生命原來咁脆弱...<br />\n唔係絕症...唔係病毒...只係中暑...咁都會死<br />\n沈晚仲食野...今日夜晚6點爬左係度"},{"pid":"935b79eaa426dafb7b2d2feac1ba8987e848c061","tid":1183252,"uid":194743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T20:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f419d1049ff0f8850ddda207afd4dc56b85be8d","tid":1183252,"uid":194743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T20:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e155b262014e15572b48c55a154bc0dcdf6838db","tid":1183252,"uid":194743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e280ec9aaafd5335a5c7b8dc465c852f4d95b1f","tid":1183252,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply